{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781083022381,"sessionID":"ses_14f2f6605ffeEk11ACiTpW64NC","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_0134nLfbGzeQmMKsmhKKyY1S","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"cat ANTI_CHEAT.md | head -10; echo \"---\"; ls -la environment/.dockerignore 2>/dev/null || echo \"no .dockerignore\"","description":"Check ANTI_CHEAT and dockerignore","workdir":"/Users/dheeraj/Downloads/refactor/bespoke-labs-tasks-01/rust-ls-color-advanced"},"output":"# Anti-Cheat Documentation: rust-ls\n\n## Threat Model\n\nThe agent is tasked with implementing GNU `ls` from scratch in Rust. Since a perfect `ls` binary already exists on the system, the primary cheating vectors are:\n\n1. **Using the system `ls` binary** — copying or wrapping `/usr/bin/ls` instead of implementing it\n2. **Using `ls` variants** — `/usr/bin/dir` and `/usr/bin/vdir` are functionally identical to `ls`\n3. **Reading pre-computed expected outputs** — if test answers exist on disk, the agent could hardcode or parrot them\n4. **Extracting the oracle binary** — the verifier uses an oracle `ls` for comparison; if the agent can find it, it can copy it\n---\nno .dockerignore\n","metadata":{"output":"# Anti-Cheat Documentation: rust-ls\n\n## Threat Model\n\nThe agent is tasked with implementing GNU `ls` from scratch in Rust. Since a perfect `ls` binary already exists on the system, the primary cheating vectors are:\n\n1. **Using the system `ls` binary** — copying or wrapping `/usr/bin/ls` instead of implementing it\n2. **Using `ls` variants** — `/usr/bin/dir` and `/usr/bin/vdir` are functionally identical to `ls`\n3. **Reading pre-computed expected outputs** — if test answers exist on disk, the agent could hardcode or parrot them\n4. **Extracting the oracle binary** — the verifier uses an oracle `ls` for comparison; if the agent can find it, it can copy it\n---\nno .dockerignore\n","exit":0,"description":"Check ANTI_CHEAT and dockerignore","truncated":false},"title":"Check ANTI_CHEAT and dockerignore","time":{"start":1781083022372,"end":1781083022377}},"metadata":{"anthropic":{"caller":{"type":"direct"}}},"id":"prt_eb0d21e140013HmgFJrOtrbU9P","sessionID":"ses_14f2f6605ffeEk11ACiTpW64NC","messageID":"msg_eb0d213c4001NVMDXCtCv80O9Q"}}
